===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[sober up]]; to [[regain]] [[consciousness]]
#: {{zh-co|甦醒|to regain consciousness}}
# to [[awaken]]; to [[wake up]]
#: {{zh-co|叫醒|to awaken}}
# to be [[awake]]
#: {{zh-co|弟弟 還 醒 著 嗎？|Is younger brother still awake?}}
# to [[realize]]; to become [[aware]] of
#: {{zh-co|覺醒|to become fully aware of something}}
# to be [[striking]]; to [[catch]] one's [[attention]]
#: {{zh-co|醒目|eye-catching}}
# to [[keep]] [[dough]] till it [[reach]]es the [[desired]] [[state]] of [[softness]], [[evenness]], etc. {{gl|after mixing it}}
#: {{zh-x|麵包師傅 等 了 麵 醒 好 了 再 蒸 包子。|The baker waited until the dough became soft before steaming the buns.}}
# to [[decant]] (wine, etc.)
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} [[clever]]; [[intelligent]]; [[sharp]]
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[gift]]
#: {{zh-x|私人 醒{sing2} 你|to gift you personally|C}} 
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} {{zh-classifier|[[frequency]] of [[sleep]]}}
#: {{zh-co|睏 一 醒|to have one sleep period|TW}}

